title: Ebro In The Morning - Real Late By Peter Rosenberg Is Out + Director Anthony Mandler
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning this episode aired on 6/3.

On this episode, Director of "Monster" - Anthony Mandler comes onto Ebro in the Morning to discuss his new film (56:00)

Ebro inquires about a suspicious MAGA vehicle (27:45), Rosenberg's album Real Late is out and it feels like his birthday (42:00), and Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segment (12:30).

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
